metadata.description: REVOLUTIONARY: Revolutionaries possess the traits of influence â€” strength, courage, and motivation. They carry the unwavering belief that people can change, are comfortable with rapid and radical shifts in the plan, and don't get "undone" by their own shifting emotions. Revolutionary leaders are truth seekers and world changers. A revolutionary's staunch conviction does not allow oneself to be concerned with a heavy workload or the opinions of others.These leaders desire to make a difference and are persistent enough to make big things happen!
